mean_cn: v.与……相配（读作/ˈkɑmpləˌmɛnt/）；补充；  n.补充；互为补充的东西；补语（读作/ˈkɑmpləmənt/）
mean_en: to add to something in a way that improves it or makes it more attractive
sentence: She is delighted that her new belt complements her dress so well.
sentence_trans: 新腰带和她的裙子很配，她非常高兴。
word_etyma: com全部 + ple满，填满 + ment名词后缀 → 全部填满 → complement补充
